## Animation Details

### 1. Moving Dot Animation
- **Duration**: 4 seconds
- **Timing**: ease-in-out infinite loop
- **Path**: Travels clockwise around card corners
- **Style**: Radial gradient with glow effect

```css
@keyframes moveDot {
  0%, 100% { top: 10%; right: 10%; }
  25% { top: 10%; right: calc(100% - 35px); }
  50% { top: calc(100% - 30px); right: calc(100% - 35px); }
  75% { top: calc(100% - 30px); right: 10%; }
}
```

### 2. Shimmer Border Effects
- **Top/Bottom**: Horizontal shimmer (2s linear)
- **Left/Right**: Vertical shimmer (2s linear)
- **Color**: Emerald gradient (#34d399)
- **Opacity**: 0.6 for subtle effect

### 3. Pulsing Glow
- **Duration**: 3 seconds
- **Effect**: Radial gradient breathing effect
- **Colors**: Emerald green with transparency

